question: How many administrative districts are there in Gyeongju, South Korea?
asked_question_translated: Ada berapa daerah administratif di Gyeongju, Korea Selatan?
answer: Gyeongju, Korea Selatan, memiliki 4 eup (kota kecil), 8 myeon (desa), dan 13 dong (kelurahan).
answer_translated_eng: Gyeongju, South Korea, has 4 eup (townships), 8 myeon (villages), and 13 dong (neighbourhoods).
